Description: Rare Fender Deluxe Power Strat in Tobacco Burst with Fishman Piezo and Callaham string tree. The acoustic bridge can be blended with the magnetic pickups into one amp or it can be separated with a stereo cord. I have added a three-way toggle that controls magnetic/magnetic-piezo/piezo outputs. Originally you could only access the piezo by lowering the magnetic volume and raising the piezo volume and vice versa to go back to magnetic. It simply was not practical. I will include the tone control and knob as well in case you want to switch it back though again, it's not a very user-friendly design. This is easily a 9.5 out of 10 in my opinion. The frets have been leveled and polished and it sports a beautiful Rosewood fret board. Kept in smoke-free home and not gigged with. Comes with nicely padded Fender gig bag. Title: Fender Deluxe Power Stratocaster W/ Fishman Piezo
